INSERT INTO `architecture` VALUES (8,'ARCHITECTURE','INSPIRED BY VICTORIAN ARCHITECTURE','It is noteworthy that all residencies overlook the extensive golf course and are beautifully designed with magnificent elements of Victorian architecture whilst encircled by a breathtaking natural landscape. The property exudes tranquility, serenity and a memorable living experience in a secured gated community living. The total project has utilized only 20% of the land area and the balance 80% is open green area space for recreational activities.\n','https://ik.imagekit.io/1xnuu0l38s/canterbury_residencies/image_11_house_for_sale_in_colombo.webp','house_for_sale_in_piliyandala','House For Sale In Piliyandala','https://ik.imagekit.io/1xnuu0l38s/canterbury_residencies/image_12_house_for_sale.webp','house_for_sale_in_piliyandala','House For Sale In Piliyandala','Canterbury Residencies has truly redefined apartment living in Sri Lanka by introducing Victorian-style architecture for the first time. It is a key milestone for Home Lands Skyline and the real estate industry of Sri Lanka.  From the exclusive range of luxury facilities to a safe and welcoming environment, Canterbury is the perfect place to call home in Sri Lanka.   \n','','','',6,'2023-02-01 06:15:26','2023-02-03 11:11:47'),(10,'ARCHITECTURE','STYLE ARCHITECTURE','As a trusted and reputed property developer, all fixtures and fittings comply with high-quality standards.\n','https://ik.imagekit.io/ewaksixzk/elixia_3cs/image_11_apartment_for_sale_in_colombo.webp','apartment_for_sale_malabe','Apartment sale in Malabe','https://ik.imagekit.io/ewaksixzk/elixia_3cs/image_12_apartment_for_sale.webp','apartment_for_sale_malabe','Apartment sale in Malabe','Meticulously designed, each space of Elixia 3C’s is aesthetically designed to the finest detail from its dimension, layout, design, colour, texture and function. The interiors are designed to highlight the resort living experience most beautifully.','','','',8,'2023-02-02 18:21:41','2023-02-02 18:44:40'),(11,'ARCHITECTURE','ARCHITECTURE WITH SECOND TO NONE','The architectural design of Aurum Skyline Residencies is a blend of contemporary and traditional elements, creating a unique and timeless aesthetic. The building\'s sleek and modern exterior is accentuated by floor-to-ceiling windows, allowing for ample natural light and stunning views of Colombo. The use of high-quality materials such as glass, steel, and concrete further enhance the building\'s sophistication.','https://ik.imagekit.io/ewaksixzk/aurum/image_11_apartment_for_sale.webp','apartment_for_sale_in_jawatta','Apartment For Sale In Jawatta','https://ik.imagekit.io/ewaksixzk/aurum/image_12_apartment_for_sale_in_jawatta.webp','apartment_for_sale_in_jawatta','Apartment For Sale In Jawatta','The attention to detail in the architecture of Aurum is evident in every aspect of the design, from the carefully curated landscaping to the elegant entranceway. The building features a mezzanine floor, providing residents with access to a range of amenities such as a modern gymnasium and multi-purpose hall. The rooftop recreational area is a true highlight, offering an infinity pool, BBQ pavilion, and a garden, providing residents with the ultimate in luxury living. The rooftop recreational area is a true highlight, offering a panoramic view of Colombo City while providing residents with a sense of tranquility and seclusion.','','','',9,'2023-02-03 06:01:35','2023-02-09 05:37:19'),(12,'ARCHITECTURE','ARCHITECTURE OF EXCELLENCE: DISCOVER THE UNPARALLELED VALUE','The architectural design of Ariyana Resort Apartments is a unique blend of contemporary and traditional styles, with a focus on sustainability and preserving the natural beauty of the surrounding paddy fields. The buildings are constructed with eco-friendly materials and are designed to optimize natural light and ventilation. The apartments are spacious, with large windows and balconies offering stunning views of the lush greenery. Each unit is designed with functionality in mind and features high-quality finishes and fixtures.','https://ik.imagekit.io/ewaksixzk/ariyana/image_11_apartment_for_sale_in_colombo.webp','apartment_for_sale_in_athurugiriya','Apartment For Sale In Athurugiriya','https://ik.imagekit.io/ewaksixzk/ariyana/image_12_apartment_for_sale.webp','apartment_for_sale_in_athurugiriya','Apartment For Sale In Athurugiriya','The engineering and structural design of the complex is state-of-the-art, ensuring the safety and stability of the buildings. The complex is equipped with modern systems such as an underground sump and overhead tanks for uninterrupted water supply and stand-by generators for continuous power supply. The buildings are designed to withstand natural disasters and are equipped with the latest fire safety systems. The elevators are fast and efficient, ensuring easy access to all floors, and the underground parking provides ample space for residents and guests. Overall, the project is designed to offer residents a luxurious and safe living environment that is both functional and beautiful.','','','',10,'2023-02-03 06:33:44','2023-02-03 06:33:44'),(13,'ARCHITECTURE','INSPIRED BY VICTORIAN ARCHITECTURE','It is noteworthy that all residential units and villas overlook the extensive golf course and are beautifully designed with magnificent elements of Victorian architecture whilst encircled by a breathtaking natural landscape. The property exudes tranquility, serenity and a memorable living experience in a secured gated community living. The total project has utilized only 20% of the land area and the balance 80% is open green area space for recreational activities.','https://ik.imagekit.io/ewaksixzk/canterbury_golf/image_11_apartment_for_sale_in_colombo.webp','apartment_for_sale_in_piliyandala','Apartment For Sale In Piliyandala','https://ik.imagekit.io/ewaksixzk/canterbury_golf/image_12_apartment_for_sale.webp','apartment_for_sale_in_piliyandala','Apartment For Sale In Pili