INSERT INTO `property` VALUES (7,'PROPERTIES','LIVE YOUR BEST LIFE IN THE WORLD OF CANTERBURY','https://ik.imagekit.io/1xnuu0l38s/canterbury_residencies/image_02_house_for_sale_in_piliyandala.webp','house_for_sale_in_piliyandala','https://ik.imagekit.io/ewaksixzk/canterbury_golf/canterbury_golf.pdf','house_for_sale_in_piliyandala','Besides the 9-hole golf course and golf training place, the property offers all the conveniences and lush comfort including a swimming pool, kids pool, coffee shop, well-equipped indoor and outdoor gym, tennis court, badminton court, basketball court, cycling, jogging track, library, party lawn, medical centre, treehouse, laundry, salon, daycare centre by Gateway College, kids play area, BBQ area, function hall, ATM facility, ample parking space for residents and visitors and many more. The world of Canterbury is everything you dreamed of!\n','SPECIFICATION','PROPERTY SPECIFICATION','Floor AreaFloor Area','Living, Dining, Pantry, 02/03 Bed Rooms, Bathrooms, Verandah/Balcony, 01 Parking Slot Within The Complex.','Supper Structure','RCC Columns, Beams, Slabs, 9\" Thick Clay Bricks On Outer Perimeter, 4\" Precast Concrete Panels/Block Walls On Internal Walls.','Pantry','Pantry Unit To Be Supplied And Fixed As Directed By The Architect Consisting Of Granite Work Top, High Gloss Doors, MDF Internal Partitioning Stainless Steel Single Bowl Single Drain Kitchen Sink With Chromium Plated Swan Neck Tap.','Water Supply','PVC Cold Pipe Network To Be Placed For Each Bathroom From Common Water Tank. Under Ground Water Sump To Be Filled With National Water Supply And Drainage Board Main And Pump To Overhead Tanks.','https://ik.imagekit.io/1xnuu0l38s/canterbury_residencies/image_01_house_for_sale_in_kahathuduwa_new.webp','house_for_sale_in_piliyandala','https://ik.imagekit.io/1xnuu0l38s/canterbury_residencies/image_01_house_for_sale_in_kahathuduwa_new.webp','house_for_sale_in_piliyandala','https://ik.imagekit.io/1xnuu0l38s/canterbury_residencies/image_0